@NODE 1. "Introduction"
  There must be thousands of AppIcon trashcan programs around. It's amazing
  that there wasn't one for me.

  I want a smart trashcan. If I throw away something from a partition with
  no trashcan (RAM disk for example) then I want it to go away. If there is
  a trashcan (like on my wife's partition) I want the junk to go to the
  trashcan directory. This is what EuroTrash does.

@ENDNODE

@NODE 2. "Distribution Info"
  EuroTrash is freeware. This means that you are allowed to copy and use it
  for free. It is not allowed to gain any profit by selling any part of this
  distribution in any form, except for Aminet CD's.

  Any re-distribution has to include all files, as in the original archive,
  without modifications.

@ENDNODE

